               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 1ra-105vb)&#xD; -
                     Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols. 1ra-12ra)&#xD; - Maṣḥaf za-wäḍʾat
                     ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols. 12ra-18va)&#xD; - Homily
                     by St Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols.
                     52rb-56ra)&#xD; - Homily by archbishop ʾabbā Sawiros (fols. 65va-67vb)&#xD; -
                     Homily by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols.75va-80ra)&#xD; II)
                     Ṣalota śǝryätä ḫaṭiʾat “Prayer of Absolution of Sins” (fols. 106ra-111rb), (cp.
                     EMML no. 427(9)).&#xD; &#xD; Colophon</summary>
